-- Asian Citrus Will Buy Juice Maker BPG Food & Beverage for HK$2.04 Billion
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-11T15:04:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/asian-citrus-will-buy-juice-maker-bpg-food-beverage-for-hk-2-04-billion.html
Asian Citrus Holdings Ltd . will pay
HK$2.04 Billion in cash and new shares for BPG Food & Beveridge
Holdings Ltd., a maker of tropical fruit-juice concentrates, the
company said in a Hong Kong stock exchange filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
